## ğŸ³ Containerized Microservice Deployment
API Gateway (8080) -> AI Core (5000) -> R Analytics (8000) ->  PostgreSQL (5432)

Each service runs in an isolated container connected through the `iassist-net` Docker network.

## ğŸ“Š Data and AI Pipeline Flow
